eper colony.',2000,4.29,211,6720,84.78,'fantasy'),(6674,9781841591063,'Eggs Beans and Crumpets',NULL,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=5aneAAAACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api','In this wonderful collection of nine stories, Wodehouse puts old friends through their paces and finds them as lively as everPage 4 of cover.',2000,4.12,224,874,54.14,'science_fiction'),(6677,9780812511185,'The Sixth Book of Lost Swords','Mindswords Story','http://books.google.com/books/content?id=iamepaEpC4oC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api','When the longlost Mindswordwhich gives mindless devotion to the one who wields itfalls into the hands of Prince Murat, Kristen, the beautiful wife of Prince Mark, falls under its spell, and it is up to Mark and his companions to save his wife and his kingdom',1991,3.81,250,1221,77.92,'thriller'),(6678,9780812513738,'The Shadow Rising','Book Four of The Wheel of Time','http://books.google.com/books/content?id=7-JfDlNcvhEC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api','Perrin Aybara must return to Emonds Field to face the occupying Whitecloaks, while Rand enters the Aiel Waste and the forbidden city of Rhuidean',1993,4.23,1007,137790,81.41,'action_adventure');
